    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That makes sense. You mentioned blockages being a problem though. In the manual, it talks about things like debris or even insects getting stuck in there. Are there specific types of things that usually cause those blockages, or is it just random stuff?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
